Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.45,0:02:54.42,TITLE,,0435,0000,0125,,{\fad(700,700)\blur1.5\pos(82,358)}{\q2}ACT.6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this place alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:58.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.  My house is just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:04.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You said this car is dorky, but I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:07.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lively, small and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Trueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:11.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A Trueno...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ride in the Trueno again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun today, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.  I'll call you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:32.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, she said.\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:52.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can keep up with Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The GT-R is unbeatable after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:04.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}No matter how good the driver is,\NI guess that's the best a dated FC can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:21.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takahashi Ryosuke,\Na member of the Redsuns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:22.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nakazato Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the team in Myogi\Ncalled the Night Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakazato Takeshi of\Nthe Night Kids...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:33.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The fastest downhill Road Racer on Myogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:38.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored to be known by a superstar\Nlike Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:42.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Night Kids' Nakazato I heard of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...was driving an S13.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is a Road Racer\Nfrom Myogi doing on Akina?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:56.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on.\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:05:01.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from Akagi, and I know we're\Nhere for the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:07.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to see the\NEight-Six I saw yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:12.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A 32 driver is going to\Nchallenge the Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:15.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,With a 32 tuned to 380 HP?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:22.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell by the exhaust sound on\Nthe straightaway and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:25.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But the outcome's pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:28.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six is no match\Nfor the 32 on the uphill...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:33.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you can't defeat the Eight-Six\Nwith your 32 on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:38.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My 32 can't beat the\NEight-Six on the downhill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:43.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be offended.  I'm just\Ntelling you my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:50.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so hesitant just\Nbecause your brother was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only an Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:55.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out if you race him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...that only I can defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:01.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me.  Having\Nsaid that, I won't back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat the Eight-Six, and\Nmake you eat your words!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Your confidence won't last long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:11.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about Nakazato of Myogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:15.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll learn that the rotary\Nis no match for the 32!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:32.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}...was driving an S13.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:36.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That's right, I changed at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, I can't pass him,\Nno matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:58.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Even if I close in on the corner,\Nhe pulls away on the straightaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}My technique as a Road Racer is better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, will I lose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:33.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can't keep up with\Na 32 with this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:39.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The best of Myogi can't defeat\Na 32, which doesn't even drift?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}A car has its limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:48.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}No matter how good the driver is,\Nit won't run beyond its capabilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...even if it's the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Good morning.{\r}\NGood morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Iketani.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:11.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We had some left from yesterday,\Nso Dad told me to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's concerned about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:25.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you've been delivering tofu to\Nthe hotel by Akina Lake for five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:32.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so secretive.\NYou could've told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:36.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't talk about it openly.\NI would've gotten in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,T...that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:44.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We were only middle school\Nfreshmen five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:50.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been driving\Nlonger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:56.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day on Akina, whether it's raining\Nor snowing, since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:59.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was early morning,\Nso nobody saw me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:04.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but weren't you scared of those corners?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:07.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared in the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:11.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but my fear was gone after six months or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:14.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,As I picked up the speed, the tires\Nwould naturally start skidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:19.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it took me another six months\Nuntil I could skid and stop as I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:23.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mastered the downhill\Nin only a year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:27.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When you do it everyday,\Nyou get used to skidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:32.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was boring... so I tried to get as close\Nas I could to the guardrails.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary people don't do\Nsuch dangerous things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought it was dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:40.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and when I'm in a good mood,\NI can get as close as 1 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,One centimeter...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:51.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really boring work unless\NI find something interesting to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:55.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought about improving\Nmy driving techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:59.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tiring, and I just wanna\Nget home as fast as I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:03.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I drive as fast as possible on the\Nway home since I'm not carrying tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you drive when you carry tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drive too rough, you'll\Ndamage the tofu, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:16.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't drive that fast on the way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:22.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad puts water in a paper cup,\Nand I put it in the cup holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:27.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't spill the water, I won't damage\Nthe tofu, even if I drive fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:32.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:35.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning, I spilled a lot\Neven when I drove slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:36.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Brakes, steering wheel,\Ngears and the gas pedal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:43.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm too rough with any of those,\NI spill the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:47.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad told me to rotate\Nthe water in the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Rotate the water in the cup...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:53.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's got something to\Ndo with surface tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:57.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The water rotates extremely\Nclose to the edge of the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:03.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I rotate the water in every\Ncurve when climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:09.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It took me a while to drift\Nwithout spilling the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:13.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Drift without spilling it?!\NCan you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:18.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to us, Takumi!\NYou're just joking, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:24.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important factor in\Ndriving is shifting the weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:27.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The drift king, Tsuchiya Keiichi,\Nsaid the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:34.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In order not to spill the water in the cup, he had\Nto learn extremely delicate weight shifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially if it's drift...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:40.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:45.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you defeated Takahashi\NKeisuke, don't get overconfident!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I'm concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:51.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,High octane.  Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:12:00.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's incredible, Bunta.  He'll go beyond\Nbeing a mountain Road Racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:02.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Thank you very much.{\r}\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, I want to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:12.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give me a ride,\Nand drive hard on Akina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to use the car\Nat this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, 'cause it's not very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:42.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need the car to go\Nto a meeting or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better think about it some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:49.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?  You sound like you\NWANT me to have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:52.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:57.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go ahead and use it, but come\Npick me up at the meeting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So you do have a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting really excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:14.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like riding one of those scream\Nmachines in a theme park.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:19.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm so envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:22.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'll be that fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:24.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready, Iketani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:27.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Takumi.\NPush it to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:29.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:37.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes a wonderful sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:41.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can never hear that from a turbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:55.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Here comes the first corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:14:00.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'd better pay close attention to see the\Ndifference, and steal his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,H...hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:03.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, the brakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:14.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}How...how's he controlling the\Ncar in this situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What's going on?\NIs this really a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's ringing at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That means he's already going\Nbeyond 100 km/h?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:33.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The next corner is coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the Eight-Six is coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:12.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.  It's too soon if he went\Nto the base of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...how many corners?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,T...three...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:37.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I witnessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:42.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...the echoing death cry on the frightening\NMt. Akina downhill...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:45.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...as Iketani in the third corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...passed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:51.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:53.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager, why're you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:58.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was a little curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:00.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:15.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakazato of the Night Kids\Nis unbeatable on Myogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:19.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't trust the skill of 32 drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the car is fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:22.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think so, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Keisuke's hatred of the 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:30.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't think it's a good idea for\NNakazato to go ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:39.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Night Kids defeat the Eight-Six\Nwe couldn't defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:43.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...people will start thinking our skills\Nare less than the Night Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:50.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how a rumor spreads, and I think\Nthat's Nakazato's intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:53.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:57.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody in the Night Kids can\Ndefeat that Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:02.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they race on Akina's downhill,\Nno one can defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody but my brother can defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:09.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That Eight-Six is so good and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:13.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:17.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't the latest high powered\Ncar defeat the Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:22.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, having too much\Npower is a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:27.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The turbo power is a welcome\Naid on the straightaway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it disturbs the control of\Nthe car when exiting a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a double-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In the case of the Eight-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...once the line is determined, it can\Ngo fast as the driver demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:40.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In a technical course, where\Nthe straightaways are short...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:44.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...an underpowered car can\Nrun at its full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:49.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So the turbo power of Keisuke's\Ncar worked negatively...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:52.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,On Akina's downhill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:58.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...the total time for using my 350 HP\Nmaximum was very limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:04.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as it boosted\Nto max, I had to brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:12.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the characteristic of the FR, which only\Nuses the rear tires to transmit the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:14.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What about a 4WD like the 32?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:21.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,With ATTESA E-TS system, which provides\Nstable traction during acceleration...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:25.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...it can use the full potential\Nof its turbo power, can't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:29.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakazato might defeat the\NEight-Six with his 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:51.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:54.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I look at you is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:56.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have another bean jam bun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:09.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When you eat a bun like that,\Nyou look like your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:13.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a sleepy headed moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:15.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:22.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you sit in the driver seat of the Eight-Six\Nand go off into the night on Akina...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:26.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang, squeal and boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:30.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the star Road Racer\Nof Akina, an admired hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?  Really?
