Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:40.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only a moron eating a bean jam bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:46.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I feel weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:47.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:53.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just during the race, but also when\NI gave Iketani a ride yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:59.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I just drove like I normally do, but I don't understand\Nwhy you guys got so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:06.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never made people so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:12.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Driving is getting more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:27.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The black 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:35.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it a lot these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he's tailgating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:39.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to let it pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.  The power difference is less\Nsignificant on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:45.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Eight-Six defeated the FD.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:11.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Small fry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:22.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He passed us on the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:33.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost scary. Its exit\Nacceleration is incomparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:40.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, in reality, an underpowered car\Ncan't overtake a car with a bigger engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:48.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}This is an incredible machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:53.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}After I changed cars, my rivals\Nbecame insignificant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:58.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I no longer had any opponent\NI could take seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:04.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Those showy drift plays\Naren't my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:09.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}With grip driving, I can push myself\Nto the limit, and thrill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:11.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Otherwise, I can't be satisfied.
